  <entry>
    <title>pytorch快速搭建神经网络简单模型</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/14/pytorch%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/14/pytorch%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%A5%9E%E7%BB%8F%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用pytorch搭建一个基本的分类模型</p><h2 id="写在前面"><a href="#写在前面" class="headerlink" title="写在前面"></a>写在前面</h2><p>本文假定你<strong>已经掌握</strong></p><ul><li>python 的基本语法</li><li>pytorch的基本语法</li><li>PIL的简单图片读取操作</li></ul><h2 id="数据集的获取与处理"><a href="#数据集的获取与处理" class="headerlink" title="数据集的获取与处理"></a>数据集的获取与处理</h2><p>为了便于下载，使用torchvision提供的CIFAR10数据集（<a href="https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html">点击</a>查看数据集详情）</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 获取训练集</span><br>train_data = torchvision.datasets.CIFAR10(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dataset_test&#x27;</span>, train=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>, <br>                                          transform=transforms.ToTensor(),  download=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 获取测试集</span><br>test_data = torchvision.datasets.CIFAR10(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dataset_test&#x27;</span>, train=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span>, <br>                                          transform=transforms.ToTensor(), download=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 将数据集打乱并使用Minibatch</span><br>train_dataloader = DataLoader(train_data, batch_size=<span class="hljs-number">64</span>, shuffle=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br>test_dataloader = DataLoader(test_data, batch_size=<span class="hljs-number">64</span>, shuffle=<span class="hljs-literal">True</span>)<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模型搭建"><a href="#模型搭建" class="headerlink" title="模型搭建"></a>模型搭建</h2><p>此处模型搭建选自某一网络模型（<del>忘了出处了</del>。</p><p>一共包含三层卷积＋最大池化，扁平化后再采用两个全连接层。</p><p>输入为维度(<em>, 3, 32, 32)，输出维度为(</em>, 10)</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">TBK</span>(nn.Module):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">super</span>(TBK, self).__init__()<br>        self.model = nn.Sequential(<br>            nn.Conv2d(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.MaxPool2d(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.Conv2d(<span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.MaxPool2d(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.Conv2d(<span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">64</span>, <span class="hljs-number">5</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.MaxPool2d(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<br>            nn.Flatten(),<br>            nn.Linear(<span class="hljs-number">1024</span>, <span class="hljs-number">64</span>),<br>            nn.Linear(<span class="hljs-number">64</span>, <span class="hljs-number">10</span>)<br>        )<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">forward</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, x</span>):<br>        x = self.model(x)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="设置常见参数"><a href="#设置常见参数" class="headerlink" title="设置常见参数"></a>设置常见参数</h2><p>详见代码注释</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 模型声明</span><br>tbk = TBK()<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 损失函数创立</span><br>loss_fn = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 优化器选择及学习率设定</span><br>learning_rate = <span class="hljs-number">0.01</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 由于adam算法在达到最优后Loss会突增，所以在大概第四轮训练结束后将优化器更换为SGD（随机梯度下降</span><br>optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(tbk.parameters(), lr=learning_rate)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 总共训练次数</span><br>total_train_step = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>total_test_step = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 总共训练轮数</span><br>epoch = <span class="hljs-number">20</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模型训练以及测试"><a href="#模型训练以及测试" class="headerlink" title="模型训练以及测试"></a>模型训练以及测试</h2><p>详见代码注释</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 使用SummaryWriters记录训练情况</span><br>writer = SummaryWriter(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;logs&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 开始训练</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(epoch):<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 在第五轮更换算法</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> i == <span class="hljs-number">4</span>:<br>        optimizer = torch.optim.SGD(tbk.parameters(), lr=learning_rate)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;##########################&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;第&#123;&#125;轮训练开始&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>))<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 将模型切换为训练模式</span><br>    tbk.train()<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> data <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> train_dataloader:<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 获取图像</span><br>        imgs, targets = data<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 正向传播</span><br>        outputs = tbk(imgs)<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 计算损失</span><br>        loss = loss_fn(outputs, targets)<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 反向传播并更新参数</span><br>        optimizer.zero_grad()  <span class="hljs-comment"># 清空梯度</span><br>        loss.backward()<br>        optimizer.step()<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 每100次训练打印Loss</span><br>        total_train_step += <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (total_train_step % <span class="hljs-number">100</span>) == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;训练次数：&#123;&#125;，Loss：&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(total_train_step, loss.item()))<br>            writer.add_scalar(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;train_loss&#x27;</span>, loss.item(), total_train_step)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 开始测试</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 声明模型在测试集上的Loss以及预测准确率</span><br>    total_test_loss = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    total_accuracy = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 将模型切换为测试模式</span><br>    tbk.<span class="hljs-built_in">eval</span>()<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 开始测试</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> torch.no_grad():  <span class="hljs-comment"># 清空梯度</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> data <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> test_dataloader:<br>            <span class="hljs-comment"># 获取图像</span><br>            imgs, targets = data<br>            <span class="hljs-comment"># 正向传播</span><br>            outputs = tbk(imgs)<br>            <span class="hljs-comment"># 计算Loss</span><br>            total_test_loss += loss_fn(outputs, targets).item()<br>            <span class="hljs-comment"># 计算准确率</span><br>            total_accuracy += (outputs.argmax(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>) == targets).<span class="hljs-built_in">sum</span>()<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 打印信息</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;整体测试集上的Loss：&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(total_test_loss))<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;整体测试集上的正确率:&#123;&#125;&quot;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(total_accuracy / test_data_size))<br>    writer.add_scalar(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;test_loss&quot;</span>, total_test_loss, total_test_step + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>    writer.add_scalar(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;test_accuracy&#x27;</span>, total_accuracy / test_data_size, total_test_step + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>    total_test_step += <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#保存此轮模型</span><br>    torch.save(tbk, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;models/tbk_&#123;&#125;th.pth&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>))<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;第&#123;&#125;轮模型已保存&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>))<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 关闭SummaryWriter</span><br>writer.close()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模型验证"><a href="#模型验证" class="headerlink" title="模型验证"></a>模型验证</h2><h3 id="验证过程"><a href="#验证过程" class="headerlink" title="验证过程"></a>验证过程</h3><p>详见代码</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment"># CIFAR10数据集自带分类</span><br>classes = &#123;<span class="hljs-number">9</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;truck&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">8</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;ship&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">7</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;horse&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">6</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;frog&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">5</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;dog&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">4</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;deer&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">3</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;cat&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">2</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;bird&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">1</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;automobile&#x27;</span>,<br>           <span class="hljs-number">0</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;airplane&#x27;</span>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 利用PIL进行图片读入</span><br>img_path = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;imgs/test_cat.jpg&#x27;</span><br>image_PIL = Image.<span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(img_path)<br>image_PIL = image_PIL.convert(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;RGB&#x27;</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment"># png有透明度通道，jpg不用管，加上可以自适应</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 图片处理</span><br>transform = torchvision.transforms.Compose([<br>    torchvision.transforms.Resize((<span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">32</span>)),<br>    torchvision.transforms.ToTensor()<br>])<br><br>image = transform(image_PIL)<br>image = torch.reshape(image, (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">3</span>, <span class="hljs-number">32</span>, <span class="hljs-number">32</span>))<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 读取训练好的模型</span><br>model = TBK()<br>model = torch.load(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;models/tbk_20th.pth&#x27;</span>)<br><br>model.<span class="hljs-built_in">eval</span>()<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 进行验证</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> torch.no_grad():<br>    outputs = model(image)<br>    index = outputs.argmax(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(outputs)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Maybe...It is a &#123;&#125;?&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(classes[index.item()]))<br>    image_PIL.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="验证结果"><a href="#验证结果" class="headerlink" title="验证结果"></a>验证结果</h3><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/tbbbk/BlogIMG/20220914210118.png"></p><p><img src="https://gcore.jsdelivr.net/gh/tbbbk/BlogIMG/test_cat.jpg"></p><p>如图，模型预测正确。</p><p>练手项目，分类正确率在70%左右，欢迎优化。</p><hr><hr><hr><p><strong>更多：</strong></p><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>pytorch官方文档：<a href="https://pytorch.org/docs/stable/index.html">PyTorch documentation — PyTorch 1.12 documentation</a><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li><li><span id="fn:2" class="footnote-text"><span>项目地址：<a href="https://github.com/tbbbk/A_Easy_Pytorch_Model">tbbbk&#x2F;A_Easy_Pytorch_Model (github.com)</a><a href="#fnref:2" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
